image.altText: Bottles labelled hand sanitizer sit on a table with other labels in front of them.

props.synopsis: The AFP are warning importers of the date rape drug known as 'bute' will face heavy penalties after more than 4000 litres of the substance have been seized in Sydney since a change in legislation in March made it a border-controlled drug.

image.altText: A woman wearing a black suede shirt sits in a large green chair and smiles.

image.altText: Andrew Giles in his office.
